Each organization encrypts their data with a separate key,
so nobody, can read it (even storage server can't)

Data is copied to a second location,
on different server, in different country
(there could be multiple locations)

Backup is prepared and sent using our "Bahub"
application that is automatically preparing
backups without any human interaction
